data.description: Welcome to this charming one-story home located in Liberty County. With 4 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, this residence offers a comfortable living space spanning 1,340 Sq. Ft. making it an ideal starter home. The family room is spacious and inviting, providing a perfect gathering place for relaxation and entertainment. The kitchen is adorned with ample wooden white cabinets, offering plenty of storage space. The bedrooms are also nicely sized, ensuring everyone in the family has their own private retreat. Situated on an expansive 11,639 Sq. Ft. lot, there is ample room for outdoor activities and potential future expansion. The location offers you direct access to US-90 and is approximately 45 minutes from Downtown Houston. Contact us today for more information!
